%%{init: {"theme":"neutral"} }%%
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Fortio as Fortio loadgen
  participant Svc as Service demo-worker
  participant Pods as Nginx pods StatefulSet
  participant MS as Metrics Server
  participant HPA as HPA
  participant Karp as Karpenter
  participant Node as EC2 nodes
  participant EBS as EBS CSI / EBS
  participant AMP as AMP/AMG

  Fortio->>Svc: Burst HTTP requests
  Svc->>Pods: Load-balance to available pods
  Pods-->>MS: CPU/memory usage observed
  MS-->>HPA: CPU metrics available
  HPA->>Pods: Increase replicas (1 → N)
  Pods-->>Karp: New pods Pending (no capacity)
  Karp->>Node: Provision new node(s)
  Node-->>Pods: Scheduler places pods
  EBS->>Pods: Provision & attach gp3 PVC per replica
  Pods-->>AMP: Prometheus scrape → remote_write to AMP
  AMP-->>AMP: AMG dashboards update (graphs move)
